text: Vanessa Grimberg (born 28 January 1993) is a German swimmer. At the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro, she competed as a member of Germany's women's 4 x 100 metre medley relay team. The team finished 12th in the heats and did not qualify for the final. == References == Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:German female swimmers Category:Swimmers at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic swimmers of Germany
